{"id":441466,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":21}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"221","ytitle":"","mtitle":"工厂短诗(三首)","ftitle":"","authors":["谢其规"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢其规"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听得懂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鎯头说些什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听得懂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗓门象雷公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话音一落山河动:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱造的喷雾器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不饶过每只蝗虫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要社会主义果实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结得又大又重!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向害虫进攻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲床咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身力气聚在一拳中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喀啷啷，一道道银光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚下一只只圆筒……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲床咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心，在把战鼓擂动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，咱执行着你的命令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲!冲!向害虫进攻!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱的阔胸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焊锡的火光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照红咱的阔胸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱的阔胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的大地都能包容——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河北的棉花，四川的稻……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准螟蝗动!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人阶级的喷雾器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捍卫着田野上的万紫千红……"}]}